description: If there were a 9-dimensional unimodular lattice with minimal norm 2, this would be its theta series; however, no such lattice exists.
references: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 416.
links: E. M. Rains and N. J. A. Sloane, The Shadow Theory of Modular and Unimodular Lattices, J. Number Theory, 73 (1998), 359-389.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
